# Terraform local cache and state
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*

# Terraform crash, logs, and plans
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log
**/terraform.log
**/*.tfplan
**/plan.out

# Local variables and override files
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# AWS credentials and local secrets
**/.aws/
**/credentials
**/config
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/.env
**/.env.*

# OS and editor files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Keep provider lock file for reproducible Terraform installs.
!**/.terraform.lock.hcl
